hackathon-requirements: Must be complete before 3:00PM Sunday March 22nd.

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: How difficult was it to create your project? Make sure to elaborate in your submission and presentation.
How useful is your product? Will it scale?
How creative is your project? Why is it different and better than similar products?
How does the project reflect your learning at the event and the educational value of the product?
